  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Art: transforming tool in 250 Colombian Children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The transforming power of art is the main tool of this project, which aims to train 250 children and young people from Colombia in theater, music, dance and communication, in a municipality that has been hit by violence and corruption. With continuous and constant educational processes, we want these young people to find in art a form of catharsis and resilience, as well as a way of life. Most do not have money to pay, so they will be free, with nutritional and psychological supplements.</narrative>
  </description>
